cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.SE, cs.FL, cs.SC 

The paper presents a notation for writing conditional equations, which is relevant to programming languages (cs.PL) and logic (cs.LO). The use of caseAD, ifAD, matchAD, and letAD expressions suggests a focus on software engineering (cs.SE) and functional programming (cs.FL). Finally, the presentation of a rewrite system suggests a connection to symbolic computation (cs.SC).
